[49m[38;5;9m- 510     [0m:[38;5;9m[49m **Model drift.** Clinical documentation patterns change. New EHR templates introduce new section naming. New clinicians bring different documentation styles. A model trained on 2024 notes may underperform on 2026 notes. You need ongoing monitoring and periodic retraining.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      510[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **Model drift.** Clinical documentation patterns change. New EHR templates introduce new section naming. New clinicians bring different documentation styles. A model trained on 2024 notes may underperform on 2026 notes. You need ongoing monitoring and periodic retraining. Monitor confidence score distribution over time (a shift toward lower scores indicates drift), track the rule-vs-model ratio (if rules handle less than 50% of entities, documentation patterns have shifted), and watch human reviewer agreement rate on flagged items. Alert when weekly average confidence drops below 0.80 or rule coverage drops below 50%. Plan retraining quarterly or when alerts fire.
